<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Climate Solutions</title>
  <link href="/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-base-100">
  <%- include('partials/navbar', { page: "/" }) %>
  <div class="container mx-auto mt-8">
    <div class="hero bg-base-200 rounded-lg p-8" style="background-image: url('/img/Explore Climate Solutions.png'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;">
      <div class="hero-content text-center">
        <div class="max-w-md">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">Explore Climate Solutions</h1>
          <p class="py-6 text-white">Discover innovative projects tackling climate change across various sectors.</p>
          <a href="/solutions/projects" class="btn btn-primary">View Projects</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-8">
      <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl">
        <figure><img src="/img/project1.png" alt="Abandoned Farmland Restoration"></figure>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Abandoned Farmland Restoration</h2>
          <p>Restoration can bring degraded farmland back into productivity and sequester carbon in the process.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="/solutions/projects/1" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl">
        <figure><img src="/img/project2.png" alt="Alternative Cement"></figure>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Alternative Cement</h2>
          <p>Conventional cement production is a significant source of carbon dioxide. Reformulation can reduce emissions by millions of metric tons each year.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="/solutions/projects/2" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl">
        <figure><img src="/img/project3.png" alt="Bicycle Infrastructure"></figure>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Bicycle Infrastructure</h2>
          <p>Infrastructure is essential for supporting safe and abundant bicycle use, which curbs emissions by reducing the need for fossil-fuel-dependent transportation.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="/solutions/projects/3" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>